Games::Trackword
================

This module lets you set up a Trackword grid, and then query it for whether
or not it is possible to find words on that grid.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module has no dependencies.

